name: The Chaplain Is In
bio:
Spiritual Care Can Help
Whatever one is feeling, a chaplain can be present to listen. Our chaplains respect, understand, and help you to uncover strengths and hopes, while giving you the freedom to share with complete confidence, trust and comfort.

Chaplains honor the diverse spiritual and cultural needs of our employees. A part of the healthcare team, our chaplains are professionally trained to offer emotional and spiritual support to persons from all walks of life. All contact is completely confidential.
